                                    style="padding: 4px 10px;">
                                    <span>Low prices</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
        
                            <p class="text-[16px] leading-7">Discover the power of local SEO and unlock new opportunities for
                                your business. Our dedicated team combines expertise with innovation to ensure your brand stands
                                out in the competitive local market. Ready to elevate your online presence? Let's get started!
                            </p>

                            <ul class="Offers">
                                <li class="mt-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-lg mr-3"></i> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</li>
                                <li class="mt-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-lg mr-3"></i> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing</li>
                                <li class="mt-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-lg mr-3"></i> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="letsTalk relative flex justify-center items-center flex-col w-full text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#06642c] to-[#02435c]">
            
