                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="features-container overflow-visible my-8 flex lg:flex-row flex-col justify-center gap-5">
                    <div class="cursor-default featureBox lg:w-1/4 hover:scale-105 p-4 rounded-3xl border-2 border-slate-200 flex flex-col gap-4 hover:bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-blue-600 shadow-xl transition-all ease-in-out delay-150">
                        <img src="/assets/images/featureIcon1.png" alt="feature Icon" class="rounded-full h-10 w-10">
                        <p class="font-bold">Intelligent</p>
                        <p class="text-sm">Our AI-powered system employs advanced algorithms to intelligently analyze data, generating insightful and impactful content tailored to your needs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cursor-default featureBox lg:w-1/4 hover:scale-105 p-4 rounded-3xl border-2 border-slate-200 flex flex-col gap-4 hover:bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-blue-600 shadow-xl transition-all ease-in-out delay-150">
                        <img src="/assets/images/featureIcon2.png" alt="feature Icon" class="rounded-full h-10 w-10">
                        <p class="font-bold">Visionary</p>
                        <p class="text-sm">Embrace the future of content creation with our visionary approach, leveraging cutting-edge technology to anticipate trends and deliver innovative solutions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cursor-default featureBox lg:w-1/4 hover:scale-105 p-4 rounded-3xl border-2 border-slate-200 flex flex-col gap-4 hover:bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-blue-600 shadow-xl transition-all ease-in-out delay-150">
                        <img src="/assets/images/featureIcon3.png" alt="feature Icon" class="rounded-full h-10 w-10">
                        <p class="font-bold">Creative</p>
                        <p class="text-sm">Fuel your creativity effortlessly with our AI-driven platform, which provides endless inspiration and expert assistance in crafting engaging narratives that captivate audiences.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cursor-default featureBox lg:w-1/4 hover:scale-105 p-4 rounded-3xl border-2 border-slate-200 flex flex-col gap-4 hover:bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-blue-600 shadow-xl transition-all ease-in-out delay-150">
                        <img src="/assets/images/featureIcon4.png" alt="feature Icon" class="rounded-full h-10 w-10">
                        <p class="font-bold">Adjustable</p>
                        <p class="text-sm">With customizable settings and flexible options, our platform adapts to your preferences, ensuring that you maintain control while harnessing the full potential of AI-powered results.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <GetStarted />
        </div>
    </section>
    
</MainLayout>
